inlikl\\u0259rind\\u0259 yenid\\u0259n k\\u0259\\u015ff etdi. Kelsier \\\"\\u00e7\\u0131rp\\u0131ld\\u0131\\\" v\\u0259 \\u00f6z\\u00fcnd\\u0259 bir Mistbornun s\\u0259lahiyy\\u0259tl\\u0259rini tapd\\u0131. Parlaq bir o\\u011fru v\\u0259 t\\u0259bii lider, o, \\u00f6z istedadlar\\u0131n\\u0131 \\u0259n y\\u00fcks\\u0259k s\\u0259viyy\\u0259y\\u0259 \\u00e7evirdi, Lord H\\u00f6kmdar\\u0131n \\u00f6z\\u00fc d\\u0259 \\u0259lam\\u0259tdar oldu.Kelsier yeralt\\u0131 d\\u00fcnyas\\u0131n\\u0131n elitas\\u0131n\\u0131, \\u0259n a\\u011f\\u0131ll\\u0131 v\\u0259 \\u0259n etibarl\\u0131 allomanslar\\u0131 i\\u015f\\u0259 g\\u00f6t\\u00fcrd\\u00fc, onlar\\u0131n h\\u0259r biri bir \\u00e7ox s\\u0259lahiyy\\u0259tl\\u0259rind\\u0259n birini payla\\u015f\\u0131r v\\u0259 ham\\u0131s\\u0131 y\\u00fcks\\u0259k riskli bir s\\u0131naqdan z\\u00f6vq al\\u0131r. Sonra Kelsier \\u00f6z son arzusunu, n\\u0259inki tarixd\\u0259ki \\u0259n b\\u00f6y\\u00fck soy\\u011funu, h\\u0259m d\\u0259 ilahi despotun s\\u00fcqutunu ortaya qoyur.Ancaq indiy\\u0259 q\\u0259d\\u0259r toplanm\\u0131\\u015f \\u0259n yax\\u015f\\u0131 cinay\\u0259t hey\\u0259ti il\\u0259 bel\\u0259, Kelin plan\\u0131, \\u015fans Vin adl\\u0131 c\\u0131r-c\\u0131nd\\u0131r q\\u0131z\\u0131 h\\u0259yat\\u0131na g\\u0259tir\\u0259n\\u0259 q\\u0259d\\u0259r, daha \\u00e7ox uzun at\\u0131\\u015flara b\\u0259nz\\u0259yir. Onun kimi, o, yar\\u0131 Skaa yetimdir, lakin daha s\\u0259rt bir h\\u0259yat s\\u00fcrd\\u00fc. Vin qar\\u015f\\u0131la\\u015fd\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 h\\u0259r k\\u0259sd\\u0259n x\\u0259yan\\u0259t g\\u00f6zl\\u0259m\\u0259yi \\u00f6yr\\u0259nib. Kel he\\u00e7 vaxt x\\u0259yal etm\\u0259diyi ustad s\\u0259lahiyy\\u0259tl\\u0259rin\\u0259 k\\u00f6m\\u0259k etm\\u0259k ist\\u0259yirs\\u0259, o, etibar etm\\u0259yi \\u00f6yr\\u0259nm\\u0259li olacaq.Fantastikan\\u0131n \\u0259n yeni ustas\\u0131 v\\u0259 m\\u0259\\u015fhur deb\\u00fct Elantris-in m\\u00fc\\u0259llifi Brandon Sanderson sad\\u0259 bir sual verm\\u0259kl\\u0259 janr\\u0131 alt-\\u00fcst etm\\u0259y\\u0259 c\\u0259sar\\u0259t edir: \\u018fg\\u0259r pey\\u011f\\u0259mb\\u0259rlik edil\\u0259n q\\u0259hr\\u0259man Qaranl\\u0131q Lordu m\\u0259\\u011flub ed\\u0259 bilm\\u0259s\\u0259ydi? Cavab \\u0259linizd\\u0259ki kitabla ba\\u015flayan s\\u00fcrprizl\\u0259r dastan\\u0131 olan Mistborn Trilogy-da tap\\u0131lacaq. Fantaziya he\\u00e7 vaxt \\u0259vv\\u0259lki kimi olmayacaq.\",\"en\":\"For a thousand years the ash fell and no flowers bloomed. For a thousand years the Skaa slaved in misery and lived in fear. For a thousand years the Lord Ruler, the \\\"Sliver of Infinity,\\\" reigned with absolute power and ultimate terror, divinely invincible. Then, when hope was so long lost that not even its memory remained, a terribly scarred, heart-broken half-Skaa rediscovered it in the depths of the Lord Ruler\'s most hellish prison. Kelsier \\\"snapped\\\" and found in himself the powers of a Mistborn. A brilliant thief and natural leader, he turned his talents to the ultimate caper, with the Lord Ruler himself as the mark.Kelsier recruited the underworld\'s elite, the smartest and most trustworthy allomancers, each of whom shares one of his many powers, and all of whom relish a high-stakes challenge. Then Kelsier reveals his ultimate dream, not just the greatest heist in history, but the downfall of the divine despot.But even with the best criminal crew ever assembled, Kel\'s plan looks more like the ultimate long shot, until luck brings a ragged girl named Vin into his life. Like him, she\'s a half-Skaa orphan, but she\'s lived a much harsher life. Vin has learned to expect betrayal from everyone she meets. She will have to learn trust if Kel is to help her master powers of which she never dreamed.Brandon Sanderson, fantasy\'s newest master tale-spinner and author of the acclaimed debut Elantris, dares to turn a genre on its head by asking a simple question: What if the prophesied hero failed to defeat the Dark Lord? 