 and your loved ones for the financial turmoil that Robert\'s rich father saw coming. In 2007, as homes fell in value or were lost through foreclosure, millions of homeowners painfully discovered the wisdom in Robert\'s rich father\'s words. Today we are all aware that the house can be a passive asset. We all know that the value of a home can go up and down. Today, we all know that a person can lose money by investing in the stock market. Today, we know that our money can lose value and even those who save can be losers. That\'s why your financial intelligence is more important today than ever before. In a world of financial turmoil, your best asset is your financial IQ. Many of our global economic problems began in 1971... when President Nixon took America off the gold standard. Throughout history, when a government went off the gold standard, an era of turmoil began. Gold and silver: God-made money. The US dollar, yen and euro are examples of man-made money. When man-made money replaces real money, turmoil always follows. In turbulent times, your financial IQ is even more valuable.\",\"ru\":\"\\u0412 1997 \\u0433\\u043e\\u0434\\u0443 \\u043a\\u043d\\u0438\\u0433\\u0430 \\u0420\\u043e\\u0431\\u0435\\u0440\\u0442\\u0430 \\u00ab\\u0411\\u043e\\u0433\\u0430\\u0442\\u044b\\u0439 \\u043f\\u0430\\u043f\\u0430, \\u0431\\u0435\\u0434\\u043d\\u044b\\u0439 \\u043f\\u0430\\u043f\\u0430\\u00bb \\u043e\\u0448\\u0435\\u043b\\u043e\\u043c\\u0438\\u043b\\u0430 \\u0447\\u0438\\u0442\\u0430\\u0442\\u0435\\u043b\\u0435\\u0439, \\u0437\\u0430\\u044f\\u0432\\u0438\\u0432: \\u00ab\\u0412\\u0430\\u0448 \\u0434\\u043e\\u043c \\u043d\\u0435 \\u044f\\u0432\\u043b\\u044f\\u0435\\u0442\\u0441\\u044f \\u0430\\u043a\\u0442\\u0438\\u0432\\u043e\\u043c\\u00bb. \\u041f\\u043e\\u0441\\u043a\\u043e\\u043b\\u044c\\u043a\\u0443 \\u0433\\u043e\\u043b\\u043e\\u0441\\u0430 \\u043f\\u0440\\u043e\\u0442\\u0435\\u0441\\u0442\\u0430 \\u0440\\u043e\\u0441\\u043b\\u0438 \\u0441\\u043e \\u0432\\u0441\\u0435\\u0